vote.title: Authorize an Interlocal Agreement with Dallas County to allow for use of the City’s Computer-Aided Dispatch System infrastructure through December 31, 2020 with three one-year renewal options - Revenue:  911 System Operations Fund $142,500 as one-time upfront cost; yearly revenue amount will be determined once Technical Design and Support Model is developed and mutually agreed upon by both parties
